OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry with some low cloud and fog
OL,9,Fpatches filtering through from the
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny overnight low cloud
OL,13,Fsoon burning off to leave a dry and
OL,14,Fsunny day. Very warm or hot.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FStaying dry and settled with plenty of
OL,18,Fsunshine, some early low cloud in the
OL,19,Feast and Central Belt. Very warm or
OL,20,Fhot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
